    "In MedKLIP, the authors developed a triplet extraction module that encodes medical entities extracted from radiology reports, their position, and presence or absence as a triplet.",
    "This triplet is then encoded with an entity translation that provides detailed descriptions of entities by querying a medical knowledge database.",
    "Even the capabilities of non-medicine-specific models are tested: Although Open AI states that GPT-4V is not suitable for the interpretation of medical images 65, its performance on multimodal medical images with or without other types of clinical data has been evaluated 66.",
